"msg":"呢排好似幾興C4D<br />\n<br />\n應該用家人數會慢慢同3D Max差唔多"},{"pid":"7a4cc76dae6341ac4975b5cd56bc13a90e4c75ed","tid":727783,"uid":74259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"若果做3d product design 一定係solidwork autodesk係傾向做建築類"},{"pid":"69355cf9757f319e8c91a417b8fe158f8a6b0f47","tid":727783,"uid":80053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T13:34:27.000Z","msg":"都唔知你想畫乜野<br />\n<br />\n畫建築野,唔會實際整出黎既野就sketchup<br />\n好簡單，基本功能中小學生都學得掂<br />\n上youtube睇番個零鐘片就識架啦<br />\n<br />\n畫完想印埋舊野出黎(自己有printer又好比檔上淘寶印又好)<br />\n就學下solidwork<br />\n個人覺得好用好多<br />\n好多形狀都易過用sketchup黎畫<br />\n<br />\n想畫人/動物果類係game入面見到嘅模組就去學blender<br />\n好難,個人覺得好睇藝術天份<br />\n不過你真係有天份畫得靚係幾值錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae882bb813d78427addfceb8df93206d8de9bac","tid":727783,"uid":85946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f324f5b2c45fcfb20e23082865ac6fd0b4ebd71","tid":727783,"uid":190181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T13:24:50.000Z","msg":"如果係想增值，論R高增值Job就梗係Rhino + Autocad，再難D就識埋Revit，想發達就學埋Catia，全世界都有人請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋其實除左Catia其他都可以youtube自學<br />\n<br />\n利申: 公司請既revit技術員每個鐘收1000+"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T13:36:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffed95d9ca275af780c07f5e9cefa94c2ab44793","tid":727783,"uid":52494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T13:38:16.000Z","msg":"你係咪想講3D modeling?"},{"pid":"64950b0093742abc2eaa74999d4d62474536243e","tid":727783,"uid":190181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ae882bb813d78427addfceb8df93206d8de9bac","tid":727783,"uid":85946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f324f5b2c45fcfb20e23082865ac6fd0b4ebd71","tid":727783,"uid":190181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T13:24:50.000Z","msg":"如果係想增值，論R高增值Job就梗係Rhino + Autocad，再難D就識埋Revit，想發達就學埋Catia，全世界都有人請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋其實除左Catia其他都可以youtube自學<br />\n<br />\n利申: 公司請既revit技術員每個鐘收1000+"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T13:36:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T13:46:54.000Z","msg":"Sketchup 始終門檻低，多人識用，難直接output做drawing （除左大陸，試過用sketchup起樓，唔好買萬科樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，公司通常用黎做quick design study，所以比錢人做既job好少。<br />\n揾錢就學Revit / ArchiCad/ + Rhino啦，識埋Grasshopper/Dynamo就係變專才鳥"},{"pid":"636a8e5811ab5f343c9a92628ef10369d1c26d76","tid":727783,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T13:50:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自問手殘，畫圖很差</blockquote><br />\n建議你學好畫圖先"}]}